data.description: A HILLTOP RETREAT IN COVETED SURFSIDE CLUB ESTATES...LAKESIDE LIVING AT ITS FINEST! Past lush perennial gardens, behold a harmony of artful craftsmanship and materials!  A Farmers porch welcomes you home. Step into a dramatic two-story foyer and begin to appreciate the attention to detail and pristine condition...truly turnkey! Columns and wainscoting define a dining room where memories will be made. An open and airy floor plan allows for flow from one room to another. Prepare meals in a dream kitchen and partake in a delightful breakfast area with light streaming in or dine alfresco on an expansive treetop deck with breathtaking lake vistas in the cooler months and the music of songbirds in lush greenery during warmer days and nights. Truly enjoy the "lake life" with a community boat ramp. Gather with friends in a spacious great room with a fireplace as its focal point. Possibilities for customized expansion are endless on the lower level that opens out to a sun-filled yard with majestic trees as a backdrop...let your imagination run wild! Upstairs, a guest room with ensuite bath is sure to delight and two additional bedrooms enjoy the luxury of a connecting bathroom. At day's end, head to the primary suite and unwind in your soaking tub, gazing up at starry skies before drifting off to sleep, dreaming of your days on Lake Lanier...A LIFESTYLE BY DESIGN!
